init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He told me that I was born with a special gift.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I look at the bee and say "I command you to tell me what you know about my father."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee then tells me that my father is the reason that I have the gift of communicating with animals and insects.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I felt a surge of excitement.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was in my room, thinking about what I should do next.
